
Central logic


Move arms out of kinect view

Get kinect data and return list
	Center positions
	Volumes

Weigh every object in list
	run weigh_object script for each object
	store in list and return list of densities to corresponding coordinates

Sort
	Create matrix with 1st row: density, second row x coords, third row y coords, fourth row z coords
	Sort matrix according to 1st row data
	Return sorted matrix according to first row data

Move objects into sorting area
	Divide preset sorting area into n spots(number of objects) 
	Create list of dop-off spots
	Run move_objeect script for each obect (pickup_position, drop off position)